{"tid":1534540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環時社評：若美國會通過《香港人權與民主法案》將遭中國全面報復","createTime":"2019-09-03T04:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T06:42:44.000Z","uid":28114,"like":42,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"e8c7758f303f9688b8eb1f18224f39aed2d465b3","tid":1534540,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:42:31.000Z","msg":"美國國會下星期一復會，預料將會討論《香港人權與民主法案》。環球時報發表社評，形容是惡意干涉中國內政的霸權法案，一旦通過並實施，中美關係將會受到新的衝擊，香港及內地的發展亦可能受相關的技術性影響，但包括香港在內的中國，有能力作任何應變，若果美國走這步死棋，中國的報復肯定會是全面，不僅限於經貿領域。<br />\n<br />\n文章指，美國現行的《香港政策法》，給予香港在經濟及金融等方面的優惠待遇，不是甚麼恩賜，雖然有利於香港及內地發展，但同樣有利於美國，並符合多方利益，只要稍微有點理性的人及國家，都不會惡意損害這個全球互惠互利的金融及經貿鏈。社評強調，中國的命運不會掌握在華盛頓的手中，華盛頓並無操控中國的餘地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1164120&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1164120%26csid%3D261_341&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=3818e76b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1164120&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"da1a43ac99220fca176993cecf52def2d0822961","tid":1534540,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:42:57.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4afcd1a2e705479cecd6467db6556928aee14151","tid":1534540,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NiokKv6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNiokKv6.gif&h=b05ab9a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03b12eb723097c41350582eec1b2000193bf118c","tid":1534540,"uid":5499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:45:27.000Z","msg":"春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429bc960ec666a13a0b3b572b0e0ff9ce5adc5b6","tid":1534540,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e5375e23dd04f0bc65b42bef65175c28e57c56","tid":1534540,"uid":28114,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:45:48.000Z","msg":"唔報復正契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b430bef174829baed074e800c8a73a5567b5b483","tid":1534540,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:45:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"30b9b5fd6cd74a4a66dd485749db841d2d1c97dd","tid":1534540,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:46:11.000Z","msg":"美帝會怕你咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43653697f0c6707b04fecc29380d244453699c29","tid":1534540,"uid":69334,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:46:46.000Z","msg":"出兵啦講"},{"pid":"3f8ff5d8b81175cab9e7800c7b761dafa67fe99e","tid":1534540,"uid":28585